OL,5, A hosepipe ban affecting millions of   
OL,6, people has been lifted.                
OL,8,FThames Water imposed the restriction   
OL,9,Ffor its 15 million customers in August 
OL,10,Fto give rivers and reservoirs a chance 
OL,11,Fto recover from a lack of rainfall.    
OL,13,FThe ban meant those living in the      
OL,14,FThames Valley, London and surrounding  
OL,15,Fareas risked #1,000 fines for          
OL,16,Factivities such as watering gardens.   
OL,18,FThe company said a "cautious approach" 
OL,19,Fwas still needed but that recent heavy 
OL,20,Frain had helped the situation.         
